{"tid":2413510,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"QR Code 填 Google Form","createTime":"2021-02-18T18:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T06:24:10.000Z","uid":351022,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"226cb7e6899788740dc684617f0508b551568564","tid":2413510,"uid":351022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"如果有個網頁識用 Local Storage 儲低名同電話，將 Google Form 嘅 Prefill URL 變成 QR code.<br />\n<br />\n咁個網頁咪可以掃一掃個嘅 QR code, 就填好晒名同電話，User 跟住只需要㩒個 Submit 制就完成。<br />\n<br />\n要加密嘅話就用 Asymmetric key.<br />\n<br />\n好似唔難寫?"},{"pid":"a2232cb7d234d1b8f2d065cb8db53343edd32d7c","tid":2413510,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:30:35.000Z","msg":"我唔好自己響屋企印紙仔<br />\n去到餐廳就咁遞紙仔咪算"},{"pid":"1141e97acd62727f9ab2716dbd435f1112f0673c","tid":2413510,"uid":36761,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:57:18.000Z","msg":"個 idea 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪即係個 QR Code 網址會變咗：<br />\n<code>www.例子.com?url=GoogleFormPrefillUrl</code><br />\n<br />\n如果曾經save過姓名電話，<br />\n只要scan門口貼出黎既qr code就會直接redirect+填好張Form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一方面，要整個網頁教店家製作呢個 qr code <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n不過我係連登都提出過用google form做登記，得返黎既評語係寧願手寫紙仔，更何況你個 idea 要save資料係第三方網頁<br />\n<br />\n所以我個po由得永遠沉底算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e595e15725f653f2575f02563300df685ceaa0","tid":2413510,"uid":162421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"你意思係咪有個QR Code, scan完去左Google form之後就save落local到？<br />\n<br />\n咁Google form有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好地地寫好少少個web再open source唔好？"},{"pid":"e9779b1042dd3f4a9a0cb7403092a798c3bebf8c","tid":2413510,"uid":351022,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d4e595e15725f653f2575f02563300df685ceaa0","tid":2413510,"uid":162421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"你意思係咪有個QR Code, scan完去左Google form之後就save落local到？<br />\n<br />\n咁Google form有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好地地寫好少少個web再open source唔好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:56:08.000Z","msg":"Google Forms 有個 Pre-fill response 嘅功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7b8rYK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7b8rYK.png&h=4801a6e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n填完之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8e5UnxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8e5UnxD.png&h=0f912662&s={SIZE}\" /> 可以 Generate 到呢條 URL <blockquote><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc4HkJNj64JQuM13ahVODnv0LGWKep8rbKiC76QEB7YP_n5hA/viewform?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc4HkJNj64JQuM13ahVODnv0LGWKep8rbKiC76QEB7YP_n5hA%2Fviewform%3F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=99049028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc4HkJNj64JQuM13ahVODnv0LGWKep8rbKiC76QEB7YP_n5hA/viewform?</a><span class=\"red\">entry.774757361=%E8%83%8C%E6%A3%84%E4%BA%86%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3</span>&amp;<span class=\"red\">entry.1391007261=99987654</span></blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n咁只要有個static HTML<br />\n1. 俾User登記資料入 Local storage<br />\n2. 教商店整特定 Pre-fill Form 同 QR Code<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc4HkJNj64JQuM13ahVODnv0LGWKep8rbKiC76QEB7YP_n5hA/viewform?entry.774757361=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc4HkJNj64JQuM13ahVODnv0LGWKep8rbKiC76QEB7YP_n5hA%2Fviewform%3Fentry.774757361%3D&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=97b6bf29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc4HkJNj64JQuM13ahVODnv0LGWKep8rbKiC76QEB7YP_n5hA/viewform?entry.774757361=</a><span class=\"red\">name</span>&amp;entry.1391007261=<span class=\"red\">phone</span><br />\n3. Scan QR Code<br />\n4. 將 <span class=\"red\">name</span> 同 <span class=\"red\">phone</span> replace 做已登記嘅名同電話，redirect 過去條 URL 度<br />\n<br />\nUser就只需要㩒 submit 就得，唔使次次人手填，都係求個方便啫"},{"pid":"9a07f97c633b4542e27992e88a899464d9c71734","tid":2413510,"uid":351022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:22:47.000Z","msg":"寫好<br />\n<a href=\"https://bbbbotty.github.io/untitled_form/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbbbotty.github.io%2Funtitled_form%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=ef192245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbbbotty.github.io/untitled_form/</a>"},{"pid":"6aad6b57b648e2815858ebbea1e8f3d8f5c77983","tid":2413510,"uid":238658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:46:36.000Z","msg":"個問題出響個redirect度，好易俾人攻擊<br />\n除咗redirect個host可信性之外<br />\n<br />\n根本無可能證明個form係屬於嗰個地方<br />\n呢個亦係安心出行最大嘅漏洞<br />\n俾人不停copy同gen QR code扮唔同地方<br />\n俾藍絲放藍店射曬啲form去黃店都得啦<br />\n<br />\n我覺得個solution調轉咗<br />\n個QR code應該係響個User度<br />\n因為要個user親身俾你scan先證明你去過<br />\n<br />\n要搞清楚主客，咩係public咩係private"},{"pid":"4ef9e6865c6d8ec49788a8d06fe63ca270d5c20d","tid":2413510,"uid":323406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6aad6b57b648e2815858ebbea1e8f3d8f5c77983","tid":2413510,"uid":238658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:46:36.000Z","msg":"個問題出響個redirect度，好易俾人攻擊<br />\n除咗redirect個host可信性之外<br />\n<br />\n根本無可能證明個form係屬於嗰個地方<br />\n呢個亦係安心出行最大嘅漏洞<br />\n俾人不停copy同gen QR code扮唔同地方<br />\n俾藍絲放藍店射曬啲form去黃店都得啦<br />\n<br />\n我覺得個solution調轉咗<br />\n個QR code應該係響個User度<br />\n因為要個user親身俾你scan先證明你去過<br />\n<br />\n要搞清楚主客，咩係public咩係private"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T20:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmo